No. 11-226 (R46-027). Larry Scott Reynolds, Petitioner v. Tennessee. 564 U.S. 1067, 133 S. Ct. 21,

180 L. Ed. 2d 940,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 5212. September 28, 2011.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Criminal Appeals of Tennessee, Middle Division, in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46.1 of the Rules of this Court.
